gift:
**Usage: `.gift <user> <amount>`
            Allows you to gift population to another user**
list:
Usage: `{prefix}list <letter or letters>`
Returns all the countries that start with the specified letter(s)
language:
**Usage: `.language <country>`
          Returns the language(s) of the country**
region:
**Usage: `.region <country>`
          Returns the general region the country is located in**
tax:
**Usage:** `.tax`
            tax your population to earn coins
flag:
**Usage: `.flag`
                            OR         `.flag <country>`
            Returns a flag of a random country**
dog:
Usage: `{prefix}dog`
Shos a picture of a dog
subregion:
**Usage: `.subregion <country>`
          Returns the subregion the country is located in**
timezone:
**Usage: `.timezone <country>`
          Returns the timezone(s) located in the country**
inflation:
**Usage: `.inflation <country> <year>`
          Returns the percent of inflation of the country in that year.**
daily:
**Usage: `.daily`
            Get 100 more people into your country every day. Has a 24 hour cooldown**
coinflip:
[] = Optional <> = Mandatory
            **Usage: `.coinflip <heads | tails> [bet amount]`
            
            Allows you to gamble with your population.**
borders:
**Usage: `.list <letter or letters>`
          Returns the countries that start with the selected letter or letters**
stats:
**Usage: `.stats`
          Returns general information about the bot such as, `latency`, `server count`, and `memory usage`**
coords:
**Usage: `.coords <country>`
          Returns the coordinates of the country. 
          A negative coordinate means south or west. 
          A positive coordinate means North or East.
          Longitude shows location horizontally
          Latitude shows location vertically
          Format: `Longitude, Latitude`**
color:
**Usage: `.color <rgb or hex>`
            Returns information about the color you entered**
aww:
Usage: `{prefix}aww`
 Shows a cute picture of an animal
meme:
Usage: `{prefix}meme`
Shows a meme from r/wholesomememes
covid:
**Usage: `.covid <country>`
          Returns information about the coronavirus for the country**
snake:
Usage: `{prefix}snake`
Shows a picture of a snake
drake:
Usage: `{prefix}drake <title> | <top text> | <bottom text>`
 creates a drake meme
cat:
Usage: `{prefix}cat`
Shows a picture of a cat
unconfigurechannel:
Usage: `{prefix}unconfigurechannel <channel>`
Allows you to stop a channel from receiving updates about the bot
hunt:
Usage: `{prefix}hunt`
Allows you to hunt animals (they go to your inventory)
changelog:
Usage: `{prefix}changelog`
Shows recent updates about the bot
currency:
**Usage: `.currency <country>`
          Returns the currency(s) used by the country**
prestige:
Usage: `{prefix}prestige`
Allows you to prestige in your country.You lose all your population, but you get more multiplier so you get more population faster
store:
**Usage: `.store`
            The store where you can buy upgrades for your country!**
gdp_percap:
**Usage: `.gdp_percap <country> <year>`
          Returns the GDP per capita of the country in that year**
gni_percap:
**Usage: `.gni_percap <country> <year>`
          Returns the GNI per capita of the country in that year**
population:
**Usage: `.population <country>`
          Returns the approximate population of the country**
work: Usage: `{prefix}work` Earn population for your country
area:
**Usage: `.area <country>`
          Returns the area of the country in `sq. km`**
changeprefix:
**Usage: `.changeprefix <prefix>`
          Sets a new prefix. User needs to have admin to use this command.**
sell:
Usage: `{prefix}sell`
 Allows you to sell items in your inventory (still in progress)
quit:
**Usage: `.quit`
            You can use this command to quit your country.**
capital:
**Usage: `.capital <country>`
          Returns the capital city of the country**
states:
**Usage: `.states <country>`
          Returns the states/provinces in the country**
buy:
Usage: `{prefix}buy`
Buy upgrades your your country
